<div id="tabs-2" class="ui-tabs-panel">
<h2  align="center">Dataset Documentation</h2>
<dd>Temperature and precipitation climatology is compiled on a 0.5° x 0.5° lat/lon grid from University of East Anglia’s Climate Research Unit (CRU). The base period for climatology is 1971-2000.</dd>
<h4>Precipitation Climatology</h4>
<dl class="datasetdocumentation">
<dt>Data</dt><dd>Monthly precipitation over land areas on a 0.5° x 0.5° lat/lon grid</dd>
<dt>Base Period for Climatology</dt><dd>1971-2000</dd>
<dt>Data Source</dt><dd>University of East Anglia (<a href="http://iridl.ldeo.columbia.edu/SOURCES/.UEA/.CRU/.TS2p0/.dataset_documentation.html">UEA CRU TS 2.0</a>)</dd>
</dl>
<h4>Temperature Climatology</h4>
<dl class="datasetdocumentation">
<dt>Data</dt><dd> Monthly temperature over land areas on a 0.5° x 0.5° lat/lon grid</dd>
<dt>Base Period for Climatology</dt><dd>1971-2000</dd>
<dt>Data Source</dt><dd>University of East Anglia (<a href="http://iridl.ldeo.columbia.edu/SOURCES/.UEA/.CRU/.TS2p0/.dataset_documentation.html">UEA CRU TS 2.0</a>)</dd>
</dl>
